{
  "bookId": "heshanggong-laozi",
  "num": 75,
  "title": "第七十五章（貪損）",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "民之饑，以其上食稅之多，是以飢。"
    },
    {
      "text": "民之難治，以其上之有為，是以難治。"
    },
    {
      "text": "民之輕死，以其上求生之厚，"
    },
    {
      "text": "是以輕死。"
    },
    {
      "text": "夫為無以生為者，是賢於貴生。"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "heshanggong": [
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 16
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "人民所以饑寒者，以其君上稅食下太多，民皆化上為貪，叛道違德，故饑。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 17
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "民之不可治者，以其君上多欲，好有為也。是以其民化上有為，情偽難治。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 13
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "人民所以侵犯死者，以其求生活之道太厚，貪利以自危。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "以求生太厚之故，輕入死地也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 4,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 14
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "夫唯獨無以生為務者，爵祿不干於意，財利不入於身，天子不得臣，諸侯不得使，則賢於貴生也。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
